    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1001239340">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1001239340" class="vote-count">2</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1001239340" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1001239340">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/madbilly/">菜刀暗夜独行</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2016-01-18</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">多年过去，本书被人记住的也就是两句台词：做人要厚道；审美疲劳。但手机压榨个人空间、沟通方式越丰富谎言就越多这两个批判性的主题，却已然被读者忽略了。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="44628207">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
